"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"bu停左啦"},{"pid":"646ffce69f837d561196d07f21f864eba93e4d23","tid":1711033,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4489a5b680baf5c69af24a5ff9d441e376af56a6","tid":1711033,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚危險叫學生返學?"},{"pid":"719383b28262f514746e72a3b948b7dbe98a5e97","tid":1711033,"uid":317019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"CIHE已停"},{"pid":"8034ff193ccaf6aa078a59c821bd4a1a7ddf8855","tid":1711033,"uid":300029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"已email去hang seng u"},{"pid":"3378abd560895c6c3f826cf47e4f7a668ca6f1bb","tid":1711033,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4489a5b680baf5c69af24a5ff9d441e376af56a6","tid":1711033,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚危險叫學生返學?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"【一人一信促請嶺南停課】:postbox:<br />\n<br />\n一連兩日，警方肆意讓催淚彈、子彈在大專院校校園橫飛，視學生安全如無物，其事後更聲言即使無手令亦能在校園執法。令人憤恨的是，學校對此至今仍無回應且無措施保障學生安全，卻稱明日將復課如常，以致校內師生人心惶惶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我們希望同學一人一信促請嶺南立即宣布停課以察安全。<br />\n<br />\n樣本信件如下：<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\nTo whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nOn 11 Nov under no circumstances of observable threats to life, the Hong Kong police force shot protesters with live rounds multiple times without issuing any prior warnings. Several protestors were critically injured by the shots.<br />\n<br />\nTransportation to commute to the campus, like MTR, Cross-Harbor Buses are often disrupted in these few days. Apart from the congestion and inconvenience , we believe our personal safety will be jeopardized in midst of this social movements. Students and staff&rsquo;s safety should always be prioritized in an university. It is necessary to suspend the school to safeguard all stakeholders in lingnan.<br />\n<br />\nMeanwhile, tear gas was fired in almost all districts of Hong Kong, including inside the private premises of university campuses. Such abuse of power by the police is not unprecedented, and has been becoming more severe and violent in the past five months. <br />\n<br />\nCurrently, the personal safety of students is being threatened. It is incontrovertible that school campuses would no longer be able to provide a safe shelter for students, since highly toxic tear gas is now spread all around the city. It should also be noted that there have also been a suspension of school in various universities.<br />\n<br />\nWe, Lingnan university students  are now in a state of desperation and sincerely urge that suspension of schools be promptly adopted until our personal safety can be ensured.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\n*YOUR NAME*<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n寄送至<br />\n:point_right: ocpa@ln.edu.hk<br />\n:point_right: ssc@ln.edu.hk"},{"pid":"550237b05e97fa224503edf39616378dedbb3325","tid":1711033,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8034ff193ccaf6aa078a59c821bd4a1a7ddf8855","tid":1711033,"uid":300029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"已email去hang seng u"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"教大同嶺大唔肯停，應該係因為淋病今日話唔可以屈服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d3a31dfcc992f7a6bb2a6ef7b6c1875945b47e","tid":1711033,"uid":247552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b825783843ae146d845c5c508a57ecb